<p class="ql-align-center">△刘飞生活照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面前一辆小车突然停下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一名十几岁的小女孩冲下车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爬上桥栏杆一跃跳进扶夷江</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女孩母亲哭喊求救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘飞与女孩父亲一同冲到桥尾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不会游泳的女孩父亲救女心切</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随即亦跳入河中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下水后也发生溺水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>父女二人情况危急</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目睹这一幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘飞迅速脱掉衣服跳入河中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">游到父女俩身边展开施救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他用尽全身力气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一手拉着小女孩 一手托着孩子父亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奋力向岸边游去🏊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>多名市民爱心接力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成功营救父女二人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时，有几位热心市民看到后 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个接一个纷纷跳入水中帮忙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘飞表示：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“看到身后有好心人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心里当时就舒了一口气”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最终几人接力救援</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>将父女二人平安救上岸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/21a47e4bb15f409ba3c9e48233ec8245.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>父女二人身体并无大碍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随后被120救护车接走🚑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而刘飞在做完这一切之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">默默地离开了现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继续回去上班</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>网友：还愣着干嘛？鼓掌！</strong></p>
